## Templates (choose by topic)

| Topic | Template | Use for |
|-------|----------|---------|
| Visual design | design-playground | Components, layouts, spacing, color, typography |
| Data & queries | data-explorer | SQL, APIs, pipelines, regex |
| Learning | concept-map | Concept maps, knowledge gaps, scope mapping |
| Document review | document-critique | Suggestions with approve/reject/comment workflow |
| Code review | diff-review | Git diffs, commits, PRs with line-by-line commenting |
| Codebase | code-map | Component relationships, data flow, layer diagrams |

---

## State Management Pattern

```javascript
const state = { /* all configurable values */ };

function updateAll() {
  renderPreview();
  updatePrompt();
}
// Every control calls updateAll() on change
```

---

## Prompt Output Pattern

- Only mention non-default values
- Use qualitative language alongside numbers
- Output must be actionable without the playground
- Natural instruction, not a value dump

---

## After Writing

Run `open <filename>.html` to launch in the user's default browser.
